"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Genesis Director of Market Insights: Institutions may invest more in Bitcoin and crypto companies in 2022 Noelle Acheson, Director of Genesis Market Insights, shared her predictions for the upcoming institutional investment in the crypto industry in 2022 at CNBC. Acheson believes that institutional investment is a strong sign of accelerating in 2022. When talking about \\\"institutional growth,\\\" Acheson mentioned both direct token investments and investments in companies that work in the cryptocurrency field and build their infrastructure. She mentioned that in 2021, 40 companies have become unicorns. In addition to this, according to Acheson, financial institutions seem to be eager to diversify their crypto investment portfolios and seek other crypto tokens besides Bitcoin, even those that are considered risky but with higher returns. Acheson said that many bitcoin miners have migrated from China to other countries. She emphasized that many of them have gone to the United States, which will bring more advantages to mining companies, including access to renewable energy and more financing from banks and institutional investors, and even IPOs.\",\"timestamp\":1640788727,\"title\":\"Head of Market Insights, Genesis\"},\"digest\":\"Ysmpw7j6OpX1Hf0mAkeSTLLEEdJyhDiM31wSpbXF3mk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xA86107D675E941db956BeCF1CF43B2E13C3ACf4f\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"f_O-FRfbl_n3TfnDFi4oh_djQJeDToqVEeEQCXF6qgw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7p7Sm0xjFjGw3FlUdoQp8Aoat8SreByW2e_I9N8MPBc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"DKXXmNzFVHGtVxAG02JkRF_guz-TT4fNOB79jlCgrWN7P9hmxxFMJ89qElbALybPq_I6OaR06OrhyijZiDRzqg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x7a93f39a04fdb962e701aac4b3df372c534bcfa46b29edeaac732644f3d4e9433b8e77545382e7ca67873ce10c6bd9052113878a66093a24e5bc3284d366b6041c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n